msgid "Email Templates"
msgstr "Email Templates"

#: admin/class-mailtpl-admin.php:192
msgid "Now you can edit your email template right in the Appearance menu"
msgstr "網站管理員現在可以在 [外觀] 中為網站編輯電子郵件範本"

#: admin/templates/partials/default-message.php:1
#: templates/default/includes/email-body.php:15
msgid "Here you will see the email content that is normally sent in WordPress."
msgstr "這封測試郵件展示了 WordPress 網站套用電子郵件範本後的郵件內容外觀。"

#: admin/templates/partials/default-message.php:2
#: templates/default/includes/email-body.php:20
msgid "The email template is responsive an fully customizable. I hope you enjoy it!"
msgstr "電子郵件範本為回應式設計且可完全自訂，希望你會喜歡 <a href=\"https://tw.wordpress.org/plugins/email-templates/\" target=\"_blank\">Email Templates</a> 這個外掛。"

#: admin/templates/partials/default-message.php:3
msgid "We would like to ask you a little favour. If you are happy with the plugin and can take a minute please <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">leave a nice review</a> on WordPress. It will be a tremendous help for us!"
msgstr "開發者希望你能幫個小忙，如果你對這個外掛的功能感到滿意，請花幾分鐘時間前往 WordPress 網站<a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">為外掛留個好評</a>，這對開發者來說是極大的幫助。"

#: admin/test.php:25
msgid "MyTheme Options"
msgstr "MyTheme 設定"

#: admin/test.php:28
msgid "Allows you to customize some example settings for MyTheme."
msgstr "可讓網站管理員自訂 MyTheme 特定的示範設定。"

#: admin/test.php:47 includes/class-mailtpl-woomail-settings.php:1584
